seo: 万户OA,文件上传漏洞,任意文件上传,漏洞检测
seo_en: Wanhu OA,file upload vulnerability,arbitrary file upload,vulnerability detection
summary: 该插件用于检测万户OA系统中fileUpload.controller是否存在任意文件上传漏洞，攻击者可能利用此漏洞上传恶意文件。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect whether the fileUpload.controller in Wanhu OA system has arbitrary file upload vulnerabilities, which attackers may exploit to upload malicious files.
